-   <span data-ttu-id="c6a25-120">`id`ist "Null" oder "void" oder "Garbage".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c6a25-120">`id` is "NULL" or "VOID" or "GARBAGE".</span></span>  
  
